groups.name: ninja
groups.title: Neo4j Ninja
groups.bio_raw:
A program designed put our Neo4j Certified Professionals in intense training to become Neo4j Ninjas. [Learn more about the Neo4j Ninjas Program]( https://medium.com/neo4j/so-you-want-to-become-a-neo4j-ninja-c14a9c296713)


>>**Task:** answered one question per week in the [Neo4j community site](https://discourse.neo4j.com/search?q=status%3Anoreplies%20after%3A14%20-tags%3Aknowledge-base%20in%3Aunseen%20order%3Alatest) or [Stack Overflow](https://neotechnology-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=1WTC0Dd0rDZwBYiRHgXJJWmj62b-vGSj5O0vCBuWeRB4-1921051683&key=YAMMID-13361513&link=http%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2Ftagged%2Fneo4j%3Fsort%3DNewest%26filters%3DNoAnswers) 
**Reward:** gain access to exclusive monthly webinars, product demos, ask-me-anything, and feedback sessions with senior members of the product and engineering teams. 

>>Track your progress:  [**Neo4j Leaderboard**](http://ninjas.neo4j.com.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com/) 

View past Ninja Exclusive Webinars on [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9Hl4pk2FsvV-naMT6t6BVfx3-dtWnMdB). 

Have feedback for product, documentation, website, etc? [Let us know](https://discourse.neo4j.com/c/feedback-requests/38/all).
groups.bio_cooked:

groups.name: ninja
groups.title: Neo4j Ninja
groups.bio_raw:
A program designed put our Neo4j Certified Professionals in intense training to become Neo4j Ninjas. [Learn more about the Neo4j Ninjas Program]( https://medium.com/neo4j/so-you-want-to-become-a-neo4j-ninja-c14a9c296713)


>>**Task:** answered one question per week in the [Neo4j community site](https://discourse.neo4j.com/search?q=status%3Anoreplies%20after%3A14%20-tags%3Aknowledge-base%20in%3Aunseen%20order%3Alatest) or [Stack Overflow](https://neotechnology-dot-yamm-track.appspot.com/Redirect?ukey=1WTC0Dd0rDZwBYiRHgXJJWmj62b-vGSj5O0vCBuWeRB4-1921051683&key=YAMMID-13361513&link=http%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2Ftagged%2Fneo4j%3Fsort%3DNewest%26filters%3DNoAnswers) 
**Reward:** gain access to exclusive monthly webinars, product demos, ask-me-anything, and feedback sessions with senior members of the product and engineering teams. 

>>Track your progress:  [**Neo4j Leaderboard**](http://ninjas.neo4j.com.s3-website-us-east-1.amazonaws.com/) 

View past Ninja Exclusive Webinars on [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9Hl4pk2FsvV-naMT6t6BVfx3-dtWnMdB). 

Have feedback for product, documentation, website, etc? [Let us know](https://discourse.neo4j.com/c/feedback-requests/38/all).
